content: Hi!  My friend wrote a fantastic song and created a video to help Kamala. Obviously he posted it on Facebook for his friends and we have been sharing. Is there a way to show it to someone on the Harris campaign to see if they would like to use it?  It would be a donation
Hi, you can post it in <#1275846770961944628> but if you're looking to send it directly to the campaign, [you can use the contact form here](https://kamalaharris.com/contact-us/)
